---
title: Brie-and-Vegetable Tart with No-Roll Crust and Pear-Almond Salad
description: This elegant tart is easier than it looks! No need to bust out the rolling pin tonight. Instead, combine garlic spread and flour, then press the mixture into your baking dish. Fill the golden crust with tender leeks, zucchini and gooey brie. This tart is delicious warm or at room temperature.

